{"tid":1585961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【十月行動計劃】十一全港換旗大行動！","createTime":"2019-09-21T18:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:44:43.000Z","uid":109462,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ffb4d089d763845e0ba848df89818551867649d","tid":1585961,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"從尖沙咀五星旗跳海、到中聯辦廁所板被塗污、再到屯門燒旗，已經睇得出<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中共係非常緊張政權象徵。</strong></span></span>嚟到10月1號呢個咁特別嘅大日子，當然要為佢贈慶，所以我正式提議舉辦十一全港換旗大行動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動目標非常簡單，就係幫社區裏面嘅旗桿換上正確嘅旗幟。通常旗桿都係打孖上，中國旗桿要由五星旗換成青天白日滿地紅旗，香港旗桿就要由抽氣扇換成黑紫荊／香港旗呢啲可以真正代表香港嘅旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n如果有第三支旗桿，可以升美國國旗以示感謝友邦支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次行動有兩個意義：<br />\n<br />\n一、更換中國旗幟象徵中共政權唔係清朝正統繼承人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無權聲索香港主權。</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二、更換香港旗幟象徵香港人擺脫中共殖民體制，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真正當家作主。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以預期呢個行動將會引起香港以至大陸社會廣泛迴響，充分反映民心思變，絕對可以成為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改朝換代嘅第一槍！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaff69b5fc87eeaf9c682f68fd037aa257bcb88","tid":1585961,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86a5a5b195b9d7156a5fd3284fa74c0a73f90f35","tid":1585961,"uid":282280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b790631067379e277eb8d6ed218cdb89d4854a3a","tid":1585961,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:12:20.000Z","msg":"【十月行動討論】抵制十一，歡慶雙十，全民贈慶！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581858\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581858</a><br />\n<br />\n【八年前的啟示】金紫荊焚旗大陸義士：「馬克思的旗」不代表中國，孫中山先生的國旗才代表中國！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585836\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585836</a>"},{"pid":"0b11f78ae269b1ae35b5195986aaa633a39e3d49","tid":1585961,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"推到全港改朝換代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006d994e8407517f7230cf8b5e53360f406d7ca6","tid":1585961,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:14:34.000Z","msg":"推到全港改朝換代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12b942421d0e7d919eeff6c65188ca0c9695406","tid":1585961,"uid":137727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"878f672532318316e1885396009bc30f22d566db","tid":1585961,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:25:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52300f4c94aae06dc4c2d8e68c778fc1195e95e5","tid":1585961,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:26:14.000Z","msg":"推到全港改朝換代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c2bf908a0480ac895f7b43aaaafdb8a340ff05","tid":1585961,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"推到全港改朝換代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb3fa6d1cd08defeb53b13c4aa291cedd05ec7f","tid":1585961,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"燒五星旗有國旗法，燒黨旗又會入縱火，燒旗不如換旗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3364f0f36866e49efb2b2863b6e7890d6a879c2b","tid":1585961,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":